quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,Kasam hai un (ghodon) ki jo phunkare marte hue dhaudte hai
  100,2,Phir (apne tapon se) chingariyan jhaadte hain
  100,3,Phir subah sawere chapa marte hain
  100,4,Phir is mauke par gard o gubar udatey hai
  100,5,Phir isi halat mei kisi majmey ke andar ja ghustey hai
  100,6,Haqiqat yeh hai ke Insan apne Rubb ka bada nashukra hai
  100,7,Aur woh khud is par gawah hai
  100,8,Aur woh maal-o-daulat ki muhabbat mei buri tarah mubtala hai
  100,9,To kya woh us waqt ko nahin janta jab qabron mein jo kuch (madfun) hai usey nikal liya jayega
  100,10,Aur seeno mein jo kuch (makhfi) hai usey baramad karke uski jaanch padtal ki jayegi
  100,11,Yaqeenan unka Rubb us roz unse khoob bakhabar hoga